<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三年级学生们不安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们想在户外玩儿，而不是坐在教室里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希金斯老师站在教室前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“春天会发生什么事？”他问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们做暑假计划！”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但现在还不是时候，凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谁还有别的答案？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开花！”劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鸟筑巢！”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。”希金斯老师说，“天气怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阳光灿烂，很暖和。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂说，充满期待地望着窗外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但有时会有暴风雨。”卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风！”卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他家离卢克家不远，只隔着两座房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“旋风或龙卷风，通常在春天发生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谁能说说龙卷风是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯又开口了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一股旋转的强风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它的形状像一个漏斗，在暴风云下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风可以带走一头牛或一辆校车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它甚至可以把房子吹到空中！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风非常危险。”希金斯老师表示同意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就是我们每年为春天做准备的原因。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们练习龙卷风来时，该怎么做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要进行龙卷风演习吗？”凯蒂满怀期待地问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，凯蒂，以后。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，谁还记得龙卷风警报的声音？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“三声警报！”卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，我们排好队，我带领大家去地下室。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到了那里，我们就躲起来！”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈！那是最好的部分！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，凯蒂。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，谁想演示一下逃生姿势？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我！”凯蒂大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请安静下来，凯蒂。”希金斯老师皱了皱眉头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卡洛斯，你给我们演示一下，怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯走到教室前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跪在地板上，双手放在头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“完美！”希金斯老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三年级学生们欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯笑了笑，回到了他的座位。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们准备好演习了！”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，把你们的数学作业拿出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都开始抱怨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>数学课之后是社会研究课，然后是午餐时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当孩子们从午餐室回来时，该上艺术课了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们来做一张我们的龙卷风海报。”希金斯老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂，请把马克笔发给大家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂抓起装满马克笔的咖啡罐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，突然响起了警报声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂一跳，马克笔飞到了空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风演习！”卢克喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墙上的扬声器发出吱吱声和沙沙声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，奥尔森校长的声音充满了整个房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“各位同学！”校长提醒他们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请马上到地下室去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了凯蒂，其他人都朝门口走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在捡马克笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去排队，凯蒂。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会的。”凯蒂厉声回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她讨厌乔伊告诉她该怎么做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三年级学生们跟着希金斯老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走下楼梯，到了地下室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他学生从四面八方进入了地下室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都趴下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一站到墙边，希金斯老师就立刻大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有孩子都趴在地上，做出了逃生姿势。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥尔森校长拿起秒表，按了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“正好两分钟。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家做得棒极了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到教室后，希金斯老师给每个学生发了一张纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们以后再完成海报。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一份清单，你们可以在家里为龙卷风做好准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们每个人都应该组织一个家庭龙卷风安全小组。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真酷。”卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雷斯龙卷风安全小组！”卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多诺万龙卷风安全小组！”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在一张笔记本纸上草草写了些什么，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后高兴地把它递给了乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊皱起眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经猜到凯蒂的笔记本纸上会写着什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是组长！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>